reference only:
SuburbMates Homepage: Master Specification (v1)

1. Core Philosophy & Constraints

Visual Identity: "Quiet Architecture" / "Editorial Minimalism."

Primary Constraint: Mobile-First Ergonomics (Thumb-friendly navigation).

Tech Strategy: Zero-API dependency for initial render (Client-side Search/Filter).

Truth UI: Strict adherence to explicit disclosures (Paid Placement, Middleman status).

2. Layout Architecture

The page is composed of distinct "Applet Windows" floating on a "Warm Bone" canvas.

Component

Height/Scroll

Visual Style

Notes

Canvas

Full Page

#F9F8F6 (bg-canvas)

Global background.

Directory

70vh (Fixed on Mobile)

White Window, Shadow-Pop (shadow-pop), Border (border-ink/10)

Vertical scroll trap prevented by "Skip" link.

Marketplace

Auto

White Window, Shadow-Pop (shadow-pop), Border (border-ink/10)

Horizontal snap-scroll rail.

Info Dock

Auto

3x Circular Tokens

Triggers informational modals.

Footer

Auto

White, 2-Col Grid

High-density link index.

3. Component Specifications

A. Navigation (Sticky Bottom FAB)

Trigger: 64px (w-16 h-16) Circular Button.

Style: Solid Ink (bg-ink) with White Icon/Text.

Position: Fixed Bottom Center (bottom-8).

Menu: "AssistiveTouch" style floating grid overlay (w-60 rounded-2xl panel).

Logic: Auto-hides via CSS transform (translate-y-200%) when a Profile Modal is open to prevent obstruction.

B. Header & Hero

Header: Sticky (top-0), Glassmorphism (backdrop-blur-sm), bg-canvas/95.

Hero Text: text-5xl to text-6xl Display Serif (Cormorant Garamond).

Search Input: bg-white, border-line, Focus ring focus:border-ink. Filters directory content in real-time.

C. Directory Listing Cards

Grid: 2-Column layout on mobile (grid-cols-2).

Card Types:

Featured: Full-width (col-span-2), Image-Left layout. "Featured" badge (Top-Left, bg-ink).

Pro: Full-width (col-span-2), Gold Border (border-gold/40). "Pro" badge (Top-Right, text-gold).

Basic: Vertical 2-Column. Image (Aspect 3:4) + Title + Location. border-line.

Unclaimed: Ghost style (Opacity 60%). Dashed Border. "Claim" button overlay.

D. Marketplace Block

Container: Matches Directory style.

Scroll: Horizontal (overflow-x-auto), Snap-x (snap-x).

Cards: min-w-[160px], aspect-[3/4], rounded-lg.

E. Modals (Overlays)

Quick View (Profile):

Structure: Full-screen overlay (fixed inset-0).

Header: Sticky Image (h-64) with Gradient overlay (from-black/60).

Content: Scrolls under the sticky header.

Action Dock: Floating glass bar at bottom (absolute bottom-0).

Protocol (Info):

Content: "Logic Switch" toggle (Brands & Buyers vs. Creators).

Toggle Style: Inactive (text-ink), Active (bg-ink text-white).

Membership (Info):

Content: "Spec Sheet" pricing grid (Basic vs. Pro comparison).

Style: 2-column grid, border-collapse, bg-gray-50 header.

4. Typography & Color Tokens

Headings: Cormorant Garamond (Serif). Class: .type-display.

UI/Body: Inter Tight (Sans). Class: .type-meta.

Ink: #0F1E33 (Primary Text/Bg).

Canvas: #F9F8F6 (Page Bg).

Gold: #C6A87C (Accents/Pro).

Verified: #0D9488 (Teal).

Line: rgba(15, 30, 51, 0.12).

5. Interaction Logic

Search Bar: Performs real-time client-side filtering of the creators array based on name, location, category, or tags.

Filter Button: Toggles a simplified category/status filter overlay (#filter-overlay).

Skip Links: "Skip to Marketplace" and "Skip to Footer" anchors provided in block headers to escape scroll areas.

6. Content Governance (Truth UI)

Directory Header: Must state "Ranked List" (implies hierarchy).

Featured Badge: Must clarify "Paid placement" in footer or help text.

Footer Disclosures:

"Products sold by creators."

"SuburbMates is a discovery platform."

"Verified indicates ABN status verified."

7. Dependencies

Tailwind CSS: Loaded via CDN.

Google Fonts: Inter Tight, Cormorant Garamond (Injected via <style> tag).

React: Loaded via CDN (UMD).

Babel: Loaded via CDN (Standalone) for JSX compilation.

Icons: Inline SVGs (No external icon library required).


---------------------

