                        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start"><span class="type-meta text-white bg-ink w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-[10px]">1</span><div><h4 class="type-meta text-xs text-ink mb-1">Claim</h4><p class="text-sm font-light text-ink-muted">Claim your studio listing.</p></div></div>
